				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Sorry for starting a new thread but figured people would be interested in the full results and the post in the Epic-PoP pet thread will get buried.
<br />

<br />
Copied the results from that thread to here and added some more I did last night for completeness.
<br />

<br />
All pets summoned with best focus available (SoAS for PoP pets, GoDS for Epic, I did to a test using Air pet with GoDS focus though aswell for comparison purposes), given full gear and the standard 2 blades, mask, girdle.
<br />

<br />
Only the tests with Malosinia are presented here, remember debuff effects Epic pet far more than PoP pets (it has no effect on pop pets ability to do damage or tank against low blue cons) in that Epic DPS is reduced without the debuff even against mobs or roughly equal level to it.
<br />

<br />
Defensive ability:
<br />
