				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Thanks for the parses, good results.  Pretty much right in line with what I have observed also.
<br />

<br />
I would like to see DPoC focused WoX around 95-112 DPS, SoM 112-125 (from behind), RS around 95-112, and CoR around 80-100 averaged over long periods of time.  Most damage mainly done in nukes and enough regen to sustain that DPS.  With his burst DPS near where it currently is, around 180.
<br />

<br />
