			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Yeah, I pulled mobs about 20 times with FBoT and Sun Vortex, and noted the %age of damage done vs. actual damage done.
<br />

<br />
eg. FBoT crit - 4340dd .. mob on 53%hps.
<br />
This means 46.01-47.00% damage done to the mob (Mob %hps are rounded <span style="font-style: italic">down</span> to the nearest integer) = 4340hp
<br />
gives a spread of 9234-9432hps.
<br />

<br />
For peak accuracy, it is actually best to use focussed nukes. This gives a better variety of damage spreads to examine for common area (wherein lies the true mob hps).
<br />

<br />
Looking at the common area in ~20 similar tests gave me the range 9373-9432 in every test (roughly 9400 +/- 30hps).
<br />

<br />
The mob is always level 55, and I picked it as it would not try to deathmarch at low hps (also give 1-1.5%aa per kill  :wink: )
<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline"><span style="font-weight: bold">edit: </span></span>Enslaved Iksar Miners (always level 55 mob) hit 157max, so it's a relatively weak hitter compared to PoP mobs. Note, I estimate DPoC air to be taking 25dps from this level 55 mob .. Kirium's logparser shows GoDS air taking 42dps from a 52 PoP mob!
<br />

<br />
Quite a fun spot to kill alone or in pet groups as Jobaber can easily handle 3 mobs with judicious use of heals/nukes and the occasional Pet Lay-on-Hands.
<br />

<br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline">note.</span>
<br />
A lot of the mob data for Chardok in Allakhazam is wrong with regards to levels.. Chardok was revamped about 2.5yrs ago and most of the Alla database hasn't been fully updated.
<br />

<br />
I am buggered with work this weekend .. feel free to pop into "Sarnak City" and run some more tests .. would be interesting to see how DPoC Epic compares on these mobs in a pet-tanking, and mage-tanking situation (to simulate group/raid conditions).
<br />

<br />
Other Chardok mobs of interest who's levels I am certain of:
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Chokidai Mangler/Sarnak Slavedriver </span>- always lvl 51
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Chokidai Bloodhound/Sarnak Slavemaster </span>- always lvl 53
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Chokidai Bonesnapper/Sarnak Overseer </span>- always lvl 55
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Foreman Mirtakk/Drillmaster Dirrhoul/Watch Captain Hirroul/Bridgekeeper</span> - always lvl 57 named mobs (sometimes enrage at low hps)
<br />

<br />
Further in but in a significantly nastier area:
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Tortured Iksar Miner </span>- lvl 56 skellies (always enrage below 10%hps)
<br />

<br />
